{"tid":2334147,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"CAMCOM終極勝訴 暗榮因侵犯專利需賠償1000萬港幣","createTime":"2020-12-21T03:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T04:40:01.000Z","uid":111253,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0c59d8ebc77fe1e0b8793769b1659d2d8118a569","tid":2334147,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:32:48.000Z","msg":"在CAPCOM認為光榮特庫摩《戰國無雙》、《真三國無雙》、《零》系列等遊戲侵犯其專利，要求賠償損失的訴訟中，日本最高法院第三小法庭駁回了光榮特庫摩之前的上訴。知識產權高等法院二審認定光榮特庫摩有35種產品侵犯專利，要向CAPCOM賠償約1億4000萬日元(約HKD$1000萬)，注意這是終審判決。<br />\n<br />\n根據二審判決，PS2動作遊戲《真三國無雙》系列等作品中，將前作光碟放入主機即能為續作追加新角色的功能，侵犯了CAPCOM的專利。<br />\n<br />\n此前在一審判決中，大阪地方法院認為恐怖遊戲《零》系列中，通過控制器震動可以感知敵人存在這一功能，侵犯了CAPCOM的專利，光榮特庫摩向CAPCOM賠償517萬日元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gameapps.hk/news/42596/CAPCOM-VS-KOEI?fbclid=IwAR3x6BEYmobhoZHGC8wMNg5c9lMy_QxCNM-nwP8c4Bp2pWR90NVjVaefOQA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameapps.hk%2Fnews%2F42596%2FCAPCOM-VS-KOEI%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3x6BEYmobhoZHGC8wMNg5c9lMy_QxCNM-nwP8c4Bp2pWR90NVjVaefOQA&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzIgDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=f69a7a07\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gameapps.hk/news/42596/CAPCOM-VS-KOEI?fbclid=IwAR3x6BEYmobhoZHGC8wMNg5c9lMy_QxCNM-nwP8c4Bp2pWR90NVjVaefOQA</a>"},{"pid":"59ded8bccb60d924bb9b2d8c2d209f57472cc901","tid":2334147,"uid":102701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:35:44.000Z","msg":"1000萬，wfc"},{"pid":"2e507c6315434c86283d67436c271b2a58d001f4","tid":2334147,"uid":200328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"CAPCOM係咪最後俾黑客屈左筆<br />\n要搵光榮回血劍?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9513b2322eff6ce0e3597482ddd484be25fa85d4","tid":2334147,"uid":181774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e507c6315434c86283d67436c271b2a58d001f4","tid":2334147,"uid":200328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"CAPCOM係咪最後俾黑客屈左筆<br />\n要搵光榮回血劍?<im